================================
VERSIONING RULES
================================

PROJECT VERSION:
  - Patch (0.0.x): Bug fixes, small improvements
  - Minor (0.1.x): New features
  - Major (1.0.0+): Breaking changes

FILE VERSION:
  - Only updated when file is modified
  - Format: // v0.0.x (JavaScript), # v0.0.x (PowerShell), etc.
  - Optional: Files can inherit PROJECT VERSION if not individually tracked

================================
STATUS LEGEND
================================

[Original]   - Original file, not modified since v0.0.1
[Fixed]      - Bug fixes applied
[Modified]   - Updated/improved
[Config]     - Configuration file (version tracked separately)
[New]        - New file in this version

